ON<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>DOT CONTENT CREATORS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out some of the great DoT content creators and streamers across YouTube! Click the link on their names (listed alphabetically) to go to their channels, and <strong>hit that subscribe button<\/strong> to get their latest videos as and when they drop:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/Cagdasdurgunn\">\u039b\u0474\u039e\u0418T\u039b\u0110\u01a0\u042f<\/a> &#8211; Titan showcases, min-maxing, Titan builds.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/BadMotherTrucker\/videos\">BMT<\/a> &#8211; Event overviews and live streams.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCwS8gWrU26mj_C8DlwK_0WA\">ChefBaseGod<\/a> &#8211; Long time player and Discord-er returns with new content.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/churritto19\/videos\">_Churro_<\/a> &#8211; Live streams, update videos and after-show gatherings.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/TheMonkeygrl\">Dee NTG<\/a> &#8211; Insights from long-time player of DoT and leader of NTG.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UC5S1d6IYSrt95MLKy4ITmMQ\/featured\">F2P Zeus<\/a> &#8211; Reactions, updates, battles, player profiles, Titan and Relic reviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCL5wIE22BiB4Fqse0VSIWZA\/videos\">Gaming on the Dark Side<\/a> &#8211; Event showcases and grind tutorials.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCFrgkLKVG3R48foLzs_c5GA\">Gason86<\/a> &#8211; Titan vs Titan content, event overviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCbYtgn5sKNLnYiIAF_DEspQ\">Godan<\/a> &#8211; Titan showcases, player showcases, games updates, opinions.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCpowjJE1kycZT4ZF6a1PsKw\">Ice Man<\/a> &#8211; The Ice Man cometh&#8230;<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCVaWZA